As the author of <a href="https://leanpub.com/mlaphp">Modernizing Legacy Applications in PHP</a> and <a href=""https://leanpub.com/sn1php>Solving the N+1 Problem in PHP</a>, Paul takes a special interest in high-quality, high-maintainability coding practices. His leadership on the <a href="http://auraphp.com">Aura for PHP</a> project reflects this interest, along with his white paper on the <a href="http://pmjones.io/adr">Action-Domain-Responder</a> pattern.
